{"tid":672272,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打跟過glo travel去北韓","createTime":"2018-05-21T00:21:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T23:14:25.000Z","uid":79927,"like":11,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"65c848c73e3ca25a9b159e00f20b6ed962f4aae5","tid":672272,"uid":79927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T00:21:48.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n小弟黎緊想跟團去北韓旅行（應該話只可以跟團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n經過資料搜集之後，歸納左兩個比較想報嘅選擇出黎<br />\n<br />\n1）係大陸報大陸團<br />\n優點：好平，連埋機票同大陸住宿最平可能六七千港紙都包哂所有洗費<br />\n缺點：行程睇落有啲走馬看花，只係去啲大型同出名嘅景點<br />\n<br />\n2）係香港報glo travel嘅團<br />\n優點：睇行程表會有好多大陸團冇嘅行程，有啲都幾吸引幾特別，例如同當地中學生交流去當地耶教教堂<br />\n缺點：團費貴，連埋機票洗費會係報大陸團一倍<br />\n<br />\n我自己其實重質多過重錢<br />\n依家都比較傾向報Glo travel<br />\n但係佢地係行程表上面又寫到戴哂頭盔咁<br />\n話行程可能會因實際情況取消更改呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果到時去到先話乜鳩都取消哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n行程變到同大陸團大同小異<br />\n到時真係喊都無謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比多一倍價錢做同樣嘅野<br />\n所以想問下有冇巴打報過Glo travel嘅北韓團<br />\n可唔可以分享下你地嘅經驗係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2a06e00f429c260c06a6139de766e0a8d85832d","tid":672272,"uid":167330,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T00:26:31.000Z","msg":"下世再見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceeca3d7d4a4e40fb5300e8d42f522c2959799d1","tid":672272,"uid":79927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2a06e00f429c260c06a6139de766e0a8d85832d","tid":672272,"uid":167330,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T00:26:31.000Z","msg":"下世再見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T00:34:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b85de8656ffc0b7f059a6589eecb8163bc05f868","tid":672272,"uid":79927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T05:44:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31b7cb6cc29191fb2be6f58ebd15fd53fa077e91","tid":672272,"uid":186445,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T06:48:13.000Z","msg":"巴打打算洗幾錢?<br />\n唔介意貴既可以TG我<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/DPRKorea\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FDPRKorea&d=roPBnFQFRfcH9bYbT%2BtJnU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=375d971e\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/DPRKorea</a>"},{"pid":"2f5f62af5744a8fa50e81e82fdd86485846e5b7b","tid":672272,"uid":79927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31b7cb6cc29191fb2be6f58ebd15fd53fa077e91","tid":672272,"uid":186445,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T06:48:13.000Z","msg":"巴打打算洗幾錢?<br />\n唔介意貴既可以TG我<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/DPRKorea\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FDPRKorea&d=roPBnFQFRfcH9bYbT%2BtJnU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=375d971e\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/DPRKorea</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T11:23:21.000Z","msg":"15000蚊內都Ok"},{"pid":"484de40588a63decf925d1b9cfbc21c94df52ed1","tid":672272,"uid":30176,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T11:30:50.000Z","msg":"其實去得北韓 全部團旅程都大同小異<br />\n因為北韓官方限制左 可以去既地方<br />\n<br />\n而glo travel 成日都會講到自已有特別唔同既地方<br />\n佢去到 人地去唔到<br />\n事實係唔係真 就好難查證<br />\n<br />\nglo travel 相比大陸團 明顯貴一截<br />\n但勝在 有個香港領隊 +成班香港團友<br />\n感覺好好多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利伸 上年跟過glo travel 去平壤"},{"pid":"337798da44bdea781dea1f88d71d53fafed85c2f","tid":672272,"uid":106271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"484de40588a63decf925d1b9cfbc21c94df52ed1","tid":672272,"uid":30176,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T11:30:50.000Z","msg":"其實去得北韓 全部團旅程都大同小異<br />\n因為北韓官方限制左 可以去既地方<br />\n<br />\n而glo travel 成日都會講到自已有特別唔同既地方<br />\n佢去到 人地去唔到<br />\n事實係唔係真 就好難查證<br />\n<br />\nglo travel 相比大陸團 明顯貴一截<br />\n但勝在 有個香港領隊 +成班香港團友<br />\n感覺好好多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利伸 上年跟過glo travel 去平壤"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T11:38:30.000Z","msg":"睇洪狗個節目佢話坐北韓地鐵三個站就要落車，我跟glo travel就坐左大約六個站，覺得真係好過出面旅行團。<br />\n<br />\n最深刻回程返大陸住一晚要團友分享下自己經驗同諗法，學到好多嘢。<br />\n<br />\n利申n年前跟glo學生團"},{"pid":"95531de51b5f31830b83fe6f2eaa38a2d7570683","tid":672272,"uid":15140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T12:48:31.000Z","msg":"GLO團係幾好 值得比貴喲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fb0265352cbee29806825432cf52d3c8f299e83","tid":672272,"uid":25322,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T14:41:02.000Z","msg":"無論參加邊個北韓團,行程都未必跟足,不過有多冇少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於報大陸定glo travel, 其實好睇你想唔想留多幾日去平壤以外嘅地方玩,glo travel特別在有搞d東部深度遊,我就好少見大陸旅行團有搞. <br />\n<br />\n就算留係平壤,glo travel d 行程都好特別同冇乜限制,可以自由同北韓人接觸,團費比貴d都值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過最最最重要一點團友都係香港人,玩得特別盡興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   同glo travel合作開嘅導遊們都非常玩得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果你想同支那大媽玩就報大陸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:今年跟glo travel玩"},{"pid":"6c79038779cc572418c4bdf036ca3303b740ad84","tid":672272,"uid":21198,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T15:04:12.000Z","msg":"自己跟過GLO Travel去北韓，感覺上同人互動會比較多，無論係團友導遊，定係當地人。我諗佢地賣點係盡量俾你感受到當地文化氣氛，唔係淨係去出名既景點影相打卡，所以睇你自己追求啲咩。雖然價錢聽落會貴左啲，但我覺得值得既，你得到既比你預計多。"},{"pid":"58a685c00c68c6474fbfb7e7be26e05303bfbfc7","tid":672272,"uid":9942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T16:32:48.000Z","msg":"比貴一倍喎講緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申無去過北韓 想過幾年後去"},{"pid":"9f876047602e203fc30542feee1b704b199f169e","tid":672272,"uid":113064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T17:01:35.000Z","msg":"大陸團啦<br />\n以前join過一間 6人成團<br />\nglo travel有既特色野佢都有<br />\n仲要平成幾千蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其中一個contact person仲要識廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a801b31c983004bf8b4a97ab73e62dc0e1dec12c","tid":672272,"uid":84163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"484de40588a63decf925d1b9cfbc21c94df52ed1","tid":672272,"uid":30176,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T11:30:50.000Z","msg":"其實去得北韓 全部團旅程都大同小異<br />\n因為北韓官方限制左 可以去既地方<br />\n<br />\n而glo travel 成日都會講到自已有特別唔同既地方<br />\n佢去到 人地去唔到<br />\n事實係唔係真 就好難查證<br />\n<br />\nglo travel 相比大陸團 明顯貴一截<br />\n但勝在 有個香港領隊 +成班香港團友<br />\n感覺好好多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利伸 上年跟過glo travel 去平壤"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T03:05:49.000Z","msg":"你個時去成團有幾多個人？<br />\ntotal使咗幾多錢？"},{"pid":"046d29319b39a4547e7c8f30bee2f0c9f3337ca5","tid":672272,"uid":84163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T03:07:30.000Z","msg":"想去但身邊無frd有興趣<br />\n有興趣個啲又覺得危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2931278dc7106a388cc6a556a3717653d5d101b","tid":672272,"uid":79927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T04:03:12.000Z","msg":"多謝各位巴打意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該會報Glo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93cbb62fc8da87401b72fe27e81cffafa59f429f","tid":672272,"uid":79927,"like"